version_description: These chords I have written to make the guitar sound more like the Ukelele part. I've given options in my tab for a fuller guitar sound, but I believe this sounds more like the original song than other tabs.
Includes all chords and is the lyrics from the artists live, acoustic version
I felt like some of the other versions were missing some "in between" chords.
Same as Version 1 but the author (self-admittedly) placed the chords improperly above the lyrics. This version also includes the chord progression for the entire song and has correct spelling.
First version. Includes all labels, specific and timed chords, as well as official lyrics (and some of the voiceovers).
